<section class="help-card help-card--compact">
  <div class="help-card__eyebrow">Before you lease</div>
  <h2 class="help-card__title">What to evaluate about this space</h2>

  <div class="help-card__grid help-card__grid--tight">
    <div class="help-card__item">
      <h3>Layout fit</h3>
      <p>
        Make sure the layout supports your workflow, staffing, or customer experience.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="help-card__item">
      <h3>Total cost</h3>
      <p>
        Ask about operating expenses, deposits, improvements, and utilities—not just rent.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="help-card__item">
      <h3>Access and visibility</h3>
      <p>
        Consider parking, foot traffic, loading access, and how easy the space is to reach.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>